data.control_text:
The entity’s top management shall demonstrate leadership and commitment to information security.

Sub-controls:
M1.1.2.a: Top management commitment shall ensure the information security policy and the information security objectives are established and are compatible with the strategic direction of the entity;
M1.1.2.b: Top management commitment shall ensure the integration of the information security requirements into the entity’s processes;
M1.1.2.c: Top management commitment shall ensure that the resources needed for information security are available;
M1.1.2.d: Top management commitment shall communicate the importance of the effectiveness of information security management;
M1.1.2.e: Top management commitment shall direct and support persons to contribute to the effectiveness of information security management and information security and conforming to the requirements of these;

